    "date": "2026-04-16 09:45",
    "weekly_narrative": "本週全球市場由「通膨粘性」與「地緣政治僵局」主導。隨著三月 PPI 創下三年新高，且伊朗談判破裂引發能源避險情緒，市場已完全排除本月降息的可能性。儘管美債殖利率持續攀升，但標普500指數與比特幣仍展現出極強的韌性，顯示市場正試圖在 AI 驅動的生產力紅利與實體經濟的高成本壓力之間尋求動態平衡。黃金則作為對抗貨幣購買力侵蝕的終極資產，報價展現出極端的強勢。",
    "next_week_forecast_html": "<details class='analysis-container'><summary>📢 下週預測：粘性通膨下的鷹派共識</summary><div class='analysis-content'><strong>⛓️ 市場邏輯傳導：</strong><p>伊朗談判破裂帶動原油高位震盪 ➔ 傳導至生產者物價 (PPI) ➔ 強化聯準會不降息預期 ➔ 推升公債殖利率與金價同步起舞。</p><hr><strong>📉 資產動態預測：</strong><ul><li><strong>亞洲貨幣 (TWD/JPY/KRW)：</strong>受韓國央行與日本官方可能的鷹派表態支撐，亞幣雖然面臨輸入型通膨壓力，但貶值動能受利差縮窄預期而有所收斂。</li><li><strong>避險成本與製造業：</strong>金價在避險需求與通膨對沖雙重支撐下將維持歷史高位；能源成本將持續考驗製造業的獲利空間。</li></ul></div></details>",
    "focus_html": "\n        <div class=\"focus-card\">\n            <div class=\"focus-idx\">01</div>\n            <div class=\"focus-content\">\n                <h4>通膨螺旋與 PPI 數據衝擊</h4>\n                <p>最新數據顯示批發物價（PPI）漲幅超預期，創下三年來最高水平。這意味著能源與原材料成本正迅速向終端消費者傳導，粘性通膨不再是理論風險，而是已開發國家退休計畫面臨的直接威脅。</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"focus-card\">\n            <div class=\"focus-idx\">02</div>\n            <div class=\"focus-content\">\n                <h4>中東局勢與利率定價</h4>\n                <p>伊朗談判的停滯成為市場壓垮降息預期的最後一根稻草。地緣政治不確定性支撐原油維持在每桶 91 美元以上，直接推動美國十年期公債殖利率維持在 4.28% 以上的高位震盪。</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
    "fx_rates_linkage": "美元指數目前在 98.046 附近呈現橫盤偏弱態勢。雖然美國 10 年期公債殖利率報 4.282% 提供利差支撐，但非美央行（如韓國央行 BOK）因應輸入型通膨的鷹派立場抵消了美元漲幅。資金在匯市中更傾向於流向實體金屬避險而非單純持有美元，這解釋了為何 DXY 在高殖利率環境下未能突破前高。",
    "tbody_html": "\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">🔥 通膨預期</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">CPI/PPI Outlook</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">持續擴張 <span class=\"status_detail\">PPI 創三年新高，原油 91.27 美元維持能源成本壓力。</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">上升螺旋</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">地緣政治緊張、AI 能源需求、供應鏈成本回升。</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">📉 利率預期</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">Fed Funds / US10Y</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">高位橫盤 <span class=\"status_detail\">US10Y 報 4.282%，市場已排除本月降息可能性。</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">偏鷹盤整</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">伊朗談判破裂、粘性通膨數據、就業市場強韌。</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">🦅 美元指數</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">DXY Strength</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">擴張受阻 <span class=\"status_detail\">DXY 報 98.046，高利差被非美貨幣抗通膨政策抵消。</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">橫盤偏弱</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">避險資產分流至黃金與比特幣、非美央行轉鷹。</td>\n                </tr>",
    "risk_html": "\n        <div class=\"risk-item\">\n            <span class=\"risk-title\">⚠️ 薪資-物價螺旋上升</span>\n            <p class=\"risk-content\">九成高齡勞工因通膨調整退休計畫，反映工資增長預期可能進一步推升服務業通膨，使聯準會政策空間受限。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"risk-item\">\n            <span class=\"risk-title\">⚠️ 債券市場的拔河戰</span>\n            <p class=\"risk-content\">市場在「軟著陸」與「長期滯脹」之間猶豫不決，殖利率若進一步突破支撐位，將對高估值的風險資產產生流動性擠壓。</p>\n        </div>",
    "news_html": "\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Is AI going to lead to 20% unemployment - or just make your employees superhuman? - Insurance Business</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMisgFBVV95cUxQaGs5U1FBaVdzb2NKQ1M2ZXVrMUNYUlNIRTF0VXRmS1RRUlRYZ1lPNFBMUEVOWmhnM0h5UmZSOEZLYW9YcjhhTV9Wb2t3amlGdmV6dThuM1hRbFVZVzN6d1ZrWU9DNkJfSVd1ek9HcGoxQ2x5eHk0dE1vZDJoZUFZbDRiNU1fUHh2UnhoSkh6YVBJNS1JYTJnSnp3VTNVS1FTLU03R1ZQOG1KTUJfR2d2aWlR?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Inflation or recession? The tug of war in bond markets - The Economist</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Nine in ten older US workers say inflation is reshaping their retirement plans - InvestmentNews</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 10-year Treasury yield hovers near 4.3% after oil price gain, sticky inflation data - CNBC</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMikwFBVV95cUxQUDNHRXBWVHlJdjZ4MmxjNWFIX1JPTjhIVm1JbmFRdmFaQVc2WGUxT3AxR2UzeXBlTUw3SGp1ZHRJT2s2Rm5yVHo3NlpVdUJacWdsb3pWWTVzNlVKVkJKUXJNUG5KYmxWeGlBUkYxdFJOQldtZm9VMXFoTnZaU3BvZEhmRmFfaHNYMUd1cmc3YjJOM00?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Wholesale inflation rose in March to three year-high - KSL.com</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMihgFBVV95cUxNRVVXQmhEMW51SjNTVDdNeUdTWDJQVVpjZGozRHgyRFlFSEhGVFAydzZyQ3Bya3cxUFN5Y01MUUJmeEdhYkRUYUp1UXRqbWFiS1dNMjEyaEJZNlFOTVk0anh4ZkpMbGhncGxKa2RsNl9BZG9zcFR5SHRBcENOZWY3Y3ZESVBZUQ?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Investors are writing off any move from the Fed this month. Collapsing talks in Iran have sealed the deal - Fortune</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiWkFVX3lxTE4tWWZwSFhQajNYUG1ObVhqMzJkdS1zcjBrci0yQm9UblZmdHExTTY4TWtIemk2QlRiSm1DdE03SXRUSUZ2ZE9KN2EyOFhCZ2xFZjFIRlZnenRIZw?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 BOK nominee puts inflation fight first - theinvestor.co.kr</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiZkFVX3lxTE1PcmdpYzdnSTBWckxQM0FmcmxiNUYzWW9Va2hlQ3B0d0R2THp1ZXpMMU9yeTlCak5OY3V6aHhycUE4NVlHZEVqUDB6eGIzcXJjNC1La1VwT3YzVjFmODVxRXJ3V05NZw?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Inflation, deflation, and the “Goldilocks scenario” - Britannica</a>\n                </li>"
